column5: Wow, i have never been so excited to go anyhere in my 16 years of my life. lol. i am going to cedar point resort on cedar lake in perrault falls and i am really looking forward to it. im hoping on good weather and good fishing.
5 days and the boat will be in the water!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Take a deep breath and try to be calm. Then thank nitroman for giving you some tips.
